@startuml terrenjpeterson_javawatch

participant "Raspberry Pi" as Pi
participant "S3 Bucket" as S3
participant "checkImage Lambda" as CheckImage
participant "Rekognition" as Rekognition
participant "labelCheck Lambda" as LabelCheck
participant "DRS" as DRS

Pi -> Pi: Capture image
Pi -> S3: Upload image
S3 -> CheckImage: Trigger Lambda
CheckImage -> Rekognition: detect_labels()
Rekognition --> CheckImage: Return labels
CheckImage -> LabelCheck: Confirm "Bean" label
LabelCheck --> CheckImage: Label confirmation
alt Bean level low
    CheckImage -> DRS: Place order
    DRS --> CheckImage: Order confirmation
end
CheckImage --> S3: Store results

@enduml